{"tid":1476352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲話要講道德，你對唔對得住班義士","createTime":"2019-08-15T19:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T01:09:51.000Z","uid":181581,"like":7,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4583c7c7e846ca9a5a12e16091447e0297b028","tid":1476352,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:26:13.000Z","msg":"［勇武和理非大和解］終極行動守則上線了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474951</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幾千正評嘅post，大概係叫大家遵守道德，唔好動武，武力只限於<span style=\"color: green;\">制服</span>，唔可以因仇恨打藍絲，俘虜（鬼）。<br />\n<br />\n前線班義士打生打死，有人冇咗隻眼，有人俾黑社會斬三大刀，有人被打到腦出血，你對唔對得住受傷嘅手足？<br />\n有6位手足了結自己生命換黎關注，你對唔對得住自殺嘅烈士？<br />\n四十幾人企係前線抗爭，而家被控暴動罪，面臨10年<br />\n刑期，你對唔對得住佢地冇咗10年嘅光陰？<br />\n<br />\n人地打橫黎行，恰你恰到上心口，你仲係咁縮沙，想同野獸講道理，佢哋會聽咩？<br />\n催淚彈都放到去市民度啦，路過都俾人拉啦，你真係覺得道德可以保到你咩？"},{"pid":"0566b088bf352afc932553122101491efbf9e60b","tid":1476352,"uid":181581,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T20:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講好咗嘅黑警死全家呢？<br />\n講好嘅見一隻打一隻呢？<br />\n原來都係呃我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbcbb5d3aa0f08b23c9b4feab0b6abac4de8a63","tid":1476352,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T20:12:31.000Z","msg":"Ban都要貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZuZ2QjY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZuZ2QjY.jpg&h=74e12458&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhKeGrE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhKeGrE.jpg&h=1b09132b&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=kW3kYkv_l3Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DkW3kYkv_l3Q&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEoGitI067o